    {
        "content": "<p>Another one..</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Ruby\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># from this</span>\n<span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map_err</span><span class=\"p\">(\\</span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">when</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"no\">FileReadErr</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">path</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file_err</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"no\">Exit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"s2\">\"Failed to launch server!</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s2\">Error reading file $(Path.display(path)):</span><span class=\"se\">\\n\\t</span><span class=\"s2\">$(Inspect.to_str(file_err))\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"no\">FileReadUtf8Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">path</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"no\">Exit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"s2\">\"Failed to launch server!</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s2\">Error: failed to read file $(Path.display(path)) as utf8.\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># to this</span>\n<span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"no\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map_err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">when</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"no\">FileReadErr</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">path</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file_err</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"no\">Exit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                    </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                    </span><span class=\"s2\">\"Failed to launch server!</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s2\">Error reading file $(Path.display(path)):</span><span class=\"se\">\\n\\t</span><span class=\"s2\">$(Inspect.to_str(file_err))\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"no\">FileReadUtf8Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">path</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"no\">Exit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                    </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                    </span><span class=\"s2\">\"Failed to launch server!</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s2\">Error: failed to read file $(Path.display(path)) as utf8.\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 492602483,
